<li>FAQ sections answering common local search questions</li>
</ul>

<h2>Results: Reviews That Transformed SEO</h2>

<p>Within 3 months of consistent review management:</p>
<ul>
<li>Average Google rating improved to 4.8 stars</li>
<li>Organic search traffic increased by 250%</li>
<li>Local Pack rankings for multiple queries achieved</li>
<li>Customer engagement and repeat visits increased</li>
</ul>

